5. For patients undergoing surgery, abrupt preoperative discontinuation of beta blockers or clonidine is potentially harmful.S11.5-2,S11.5-13

III: Harm

B-NR

6. Beta blockers should not be started on the day of surgery in beta blocker–naïve patients.S11.5-14

Intraoperative

7. Patients with intraoperative

hypertension should be managed with

I

C-EO

intravenous medications (Table 19) until

